# Squad FE Dashboards + Reports

## Dominio

Dashboards configuraveis com drag-and-drop e relatorios cross-departamento no browser. Features: `src/features/dashboards/`, `src/features/reports/`.

**Fonte de verdade:** PLANO.md Tela Paineis, Rotas /paineis/** e /relatorios/**, Fase 7D stories F7D-1, F7D-2
**Fase PLANO:** F7D (construcao) + ownership continuo

