## Nota tecnica

- 8 tipos de card: KPI_NUMBER, BAR_CHART, LINE_CHART, PIE_CHART, DONUT, AREA_CHART, STACKED_BAR, TABLE
- Layout grid com posicao (x, y) e dimensoes (w, h)
- Cards fazem query nos dados existentes (Orders, AR, AP, etc) — nao armazenam dados proprios

---

## Interface com Outros Squads

De quem depende: Squad FE Shell, Squad Dashboards (backend API /dashboards/**), Squad Reports (backend API /reports/**).

